nistration (ILEA) or the Lieutenant's Course at the Caruth Police Institute can receive credit toward the Graduate Academic Certificate in Police Management for completing one of these training programs.  Learn more.  Please update contact information to the following: Please contact Dr. Brooke Miller, Graduate Certificate in Police Executive Leadership Program Advisor, for additional questions or information at Brooke.Miller@unt.edu or (940) 565-2562.  For information regarding gainful employment data,  click here.                       Visit Us    Chilton Hall 265 [map]        Mail Us Criminal Justice   1155 Union Circle #305130   Denton,       TX 76203-5017      Contact Us  Phone: (940) 565-2562 Fax: (940) 565-2548 Email: D'Ann.Hammett@unt.edu            Last updated April 12, 2017   Disclaimer         |         AA/EOE/ADA         |         Privacy          |          Electronic Accessibility         |         State of Texas Online         |         Emergency Preparedness         |         THECB Online Resume System Student Consumer Information         |         UNT Compliance Hotline         |         Governors Committee on People with Disabilities         |         Texas Veterans Portal         |         UNT Home                         
